&lt;p&gt;Auticons is an icon font and CSS set that harnesses the awesome power of attribute selectors. It places resolution independent icons before or after any hyperlink with an href that matches a certain, expected pattern. In other words, it&#39;s an &lt;em&gt;automatic&lt;/em&gt; icon font.&lt;/p&gt;
