&lt;section class=&quot;project&quot;&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Paragrabbr&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I use Paragrabbr &lt;em&gt;a lot&lt;/em&gt;. It&#39;s a lorem ipsum generator I wrote in AngularJS which includes special punctuation &amp;mdash; like em dashes &amp;mdash; and phrasing elements like &lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;a&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;strong&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt; and even &lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;kbd&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;. Helps you get your type design detail right.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div aria-label=&quot;external links&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://paragrabbr.heydonworks.com/&quot;&gt;Use Paragrabbr&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
